    <entry>
      <title>如何使用ExpressVPN代理上网</title>
      <link href="/2023/02/21/How-to-use-expressvpn/"/>
      <url>/2023/02/21/How-to-use-expressvpn/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>ExpressVPN是众多传统vpn服务商中比较知名的一个品牌。他家产品翻墙速度快，面对新的防火墙策略也能比较快应对。购买15个月的话平均每个月不到7美元，价格也比较合适。同时支持5台设备，可以多人均摊就更划算了。一个月内不满意还可以全额退款，这里就试试它了。</p><h1 id="购买ExpressVPN服务"><a href="#购买ExpressVPN服务" class="headerlink" title="购买ExpressVPN服务"></a>购买ExpressVPN服务</h1><p>首先访问官网，<a href="https://www.expressvpn.com/%EF%BC%8C%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%90%88%E9%80%82%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%97%E9%A4%90%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E8%B4%AD%E4%B9%B0%E3%80%82%E8%BF%99%E9%87%8C%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E4%BA%8612%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%97%E9%A4%90%E3%80%82">https://www.expressvpn.com/，选择合适的套餐进行购买。这里选择了12个月的套餐。</a><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn1.png"><br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn2.png"></p><p>输入邮箱和支付信息，点“Join Now”就买好了。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn3.png"></p><p>等待系统处理。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn4.png"></p><p>修改账户密码。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn5.png"></p><p>系统会跳到到设置页面，页面上的激活码很重要，用于激活应用。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn6.png"></p><h1 id="安装电脑端"><a href="#安装电脑端" class="headerlink" title="安装电脑端"></a>安装电脑端</h1><p>下面以Mac电脑为例进行应用安装。选择Mac，点击Download，下载对应的PKG文件。下载后双击文件安装。<br>打开ExpressVPN应用，根据界面提示输入激活码，一路点击确定或继续，最终进入到主页面。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn7.png"></p><p>多等一会时间，等待连接完成。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn8.png"></p><h1 id="安装手机端"><a href="#安装手机端" class="headerlink" title="安装手机端"></a>安装手机端</h1><p>如果是手机端需要连接VPN，则需要下手机端的APP。<br>以Iphone为例，ExpressVPN在大陆区搜不到，需要将App Store账号切换成如美区AppleID进行下载。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn9.png"></p><p>下载后打开APP，点击Sign in进行账号登陆。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn10.png"></p><p>看过条款内容后，点按钮同意条款。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn11.png"></p><p>接下来ExpressVPN会添加手机的VPN设置，点击“允许”进行授权。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn12.png"></p><p>输入手机密码，完成授权。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn13.png"></p><p>应用询问允不允许它发通知给用户。OK则同意，否则不同意，请按需选择。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn14.png"></p><p>如果选择同意，应用会调起系统通知提示，按需选择。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn15.png"></p><p>应用询问是否愿意分享使用数据，帮助提升应用。这里也是按心意选择，怕麻烦就“No thanks”了。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn16.png"></p><p>设置完成后进入主界面，可以看到中间有个开关图标的按钮。Not connected则是没链接，点击按钮尝试连接。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn17.png"></p><p>显示Connected，则表示连接成功。一开始连接可能会花较长时间，请耐心等待一会。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn18.png"></p><p>如果想了解ExpressVPN做了哪些VPN设置。可以打开手机的“设置”&#x3D;&gt;“VPN”进行查看，VPN状态是打开的，连接的是ExpressVPN Lightway。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn19.png"></p><p>接下来验证一下是否能翻墙。比如下载Youtube，看看视频能不能正常播发。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn20.png"></p><p>打开APP，视频能正常播放。<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/lattefox/cloud@master/images/expressvpn/expressvpn21.png"></p><p>翻墙成功，可以科学上网了！</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
